"     David C Whitcomb, MD, PhD",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"UTD.htm?28/14/28903/contributors\">",
"     Stanley W Ashley, MD",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"   </div>",
